Definition: truck whose contents can be emptied without handling
Example: the front end of the platform can be pneumatically raised so that the load is discharged by gravity
Synonyms: dumper, verb, motion, dump, tipper_truck, tipper_lorry, tip_truck, tipper, tip, truck, whose, contents, can, be, emptied, without, handling, the, front, end, of, platform, pneumatically, raised, so, that, load, is, discharged, by, gravity
Category: noun.artifact
